title: No. 7 Michigan St stuns No. 12 Michigan 27-23 on final play
text: > Top News No. 7 Michigan St stuns No. 12 Michigan 27-23 on final play Michigan State defensive back Jalen Watts-Jackson (20) runs towards the end zone after recovering a fumbled snap on a punt in the closing seconds of the second half of an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Ann Arbor, Mich. Watts-Jackson lumbered 38 yards for a touchdown on the final play of the game, giving No. 7 Michigan State a shocking 27-23 win over No. 12 Michigan(AP Photo/Carlos Osorio)
